{"id":3039,"date":"2025-05-16T15:17:02","date_gmt":"2025-05-16T08:17:02","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/?post_type=product&#038;p=3039"},"modified":"2025-12-25T16:19:01","modified_gmt":"2025-12-25T09:19:01","slug":"peel-hoa-hoc-nam","status":"publish","type":"product","link":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/peel-hoa-hoc-nam\/","title":{"rendered":"Peel h\u00f3a h\u1ecdc n\u00e1m"},"content":{"rendered":"<p><em>Li\u1ec7u tr\u00ecnh chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p d\u00e0nh cho da n\u00e1m \u0111i k\u00e8m l\u1ed7 ch\u00e2n l\u00f4ng to, da nhi\u1ec1u m\u1ee5n \u1ea9n, n\u1ec1n da s\u1ea7n s\u00f9i th\u00f4 r\u00e1p, th\u00e2m s\u1ea1m nh\u1eb9, kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec1u m\u00e0u, l\u00e3o ho\u00e1 nh\u1eb9.<\/em><\/p>\n<h3><em>L\u1ee3i \u00edch ch\u00ednh:<\/em><\/h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Gi\u1ea3m n\u00e1m, l\u00e0m s\u00e1ng v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec1u m\u00e0u da b\u1eb1ng c\u00e1ch lo\u1ea1i b\u1ecf t\u1ebf b\u00e0o ch\u1ee9a melanin.<\/li>\n<li>Tr\u1ebb h\u00f3a da k\u00edch th\u00edch s\u1ea3n sinh collagen, elastin, gi\u1ea3m n\u1ebfp nh\u0103n, ng\u1eeba l\u00e3o h\u00f3a.<\/li>\n<li>H\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 tr\u1ecb m\u1ee5n gom c\u1ed3i, \u0111\u1ea9y m\u1ee5n v\u00e0 c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n b\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t da.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h3><em>Chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n:<\/em><\/h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Chemical peel &#8211; s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng c\u00e1c acid h\u1eefu c\u01a1 n\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9 th\u00edch h\u1ee3p, thay m\u1edbi t\u1ebf b\u00e0o k\u00edch th\u00edch t\u1ebf b\u00e0o da<br \/>\nbong tr\u00f3c l\u1edbp t\u1ebf b\u00e0o da ch\u1ebft b\u00ean ngo\u00e0i, lo\u1ea1i b\u1ecf t\u1ebf b\u00e0o ch\u1ee9a h\u1eafc s\u1eafc t\u1ed1 melanin, gi\u1ea3m n\u00e1m s\u1ea1m.<\/li>\n<li>Gi\u1ea3m n\u00e1m, m\u1edd th\u00e2m s\u1ea1m, t\u00e1i t\u1ea1o ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i da m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd v\u1edbi GSC Alpha Arbutin Ultra Cream<br \/>\nch\u1ee9a Alpha Arbutin 7%, c\u00f9ng 03 c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 ti\u00ean ti\u1ebfn nh\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n nay: C\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 Nano, Oxy ho\u00e1 k\u00e9p v\u00e0 Exosome.<\/li>\n<li>K\u1ebft h\u1ee3p b\u1ed9 s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m d\u01b0\u1ee1ng tr\u1eafng ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i da, duy tr\u00ec tr\u1ea1ng th\u00e1i da m\u1ecbn m\u00e0ng, t\u01b0\u01a1i tr\u1ebb.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h3><em>Th\u1eddi gian li\u1ec7u tr\u00ecnh:<\/em><\/h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n t\u1eeb 45 ph\u00fat \u0111\u1ebfn 01 ti\u1ebfng.<\/li>\n<li>M\u1ed9t li\u1ec7u tr\u00ecnh \u0111i\u1ec1u tr\u1ecb th\u01b0\u1eddng l\u00e0 03 &#8211; 05 bu\u1ed5i,<br \/>\nkho\u1ea3ng c\u00e1ch gi\u1eefa c\u00e1c bu\u1ed5i t\u1eeb 21 &#8211; 30 ng\u00e0y.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p><em>Li\u1ec7u tr\u00ecnh chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p d\u00e0nh cho da n\u00e1m \u0111i k\u00e8m l\u1ed7 ch\u00e2n l\u00f4ng to, da nhi\u1ec1u m\u1ee5n \u1ea9n, n\u1ec1n da s\u1ea7n s\u00f9i th\u00f4 r\u00e1p, th\u00e2m s\u1ea1m nh\u1eb9, kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec1u m\u00e0u, l\u00e3o ho\u00e1 nh\u1eb9.<\/em><\/p>\n","protected":false},"featured_media":3551,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"closed","template":"","meta":{"_acf_changed":false},"product_brand":[],"product_cat":[33],"product_tag":[],"class_list":{"0":"post-3039","1":"product","2":"type-product","3":"status-publish","4":"has-post-thumbnail","6":"product_cat-peel","8":"first","9":"instock","10":"virtual","11":"product-type-simple"},"acf":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/product\/3039","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/product"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/product"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=3039"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/3551"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=3039"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"product_brand","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/produc